title: Private Exporters Report Sales Activity for China (FAS - Foreign Agricultural Service)
text: ( Source : FAS - Foreign Agricultural Service ) WASHINGTON, Oct. 14 , 2015-Private exporters reported to the U.S. Department of Agriculture export sales of 235, 000 metric tons of soybeans for delivery to China during the 2015 /2016 marketing
